msgstr "Society Speaks hilft, das zu korrigieren, indem es:"

#: app/templates/about.html:250
msgid "Reducing knee-jerk reactions"
msgstr "Überstürzte Reaktionen reduziert"

#: app/templates/about.html:251
msgid "Making disagreement less hostile"
msgstr "Uneinigkeit weniger feindselig macht"

#: app/templates/about.html:252
msgid "Revealing common ground without erasing difference"
msgstr "Gemeinsamkeiten offenlegt, ohne Unterschiede zu verwischen"

#: app/templates/about.html:253
msgid "Showing where compromise is possible and where it is not"
msgstr "Zeigt, wo Kompromisse möglich sind und wo nicht"

#: app/templates/about.html:256
msgid ""
"This kind of understanding is a prerequisite for solving real-world "
"problems."
msgstr ""
"Dieses Verständnis ist eine Voraussetzung für die Lösung echter Probleme."

#: app/templates/about.html:261
msgid "For Policymakers and Civic Leaders"
