#: app/templates/about.html:263
msgid ""
"Society Speaks does not claim to produce policy by itself. What it produces "
"is something more fundamental:"
msgstr ""
"Society Speaks behauptet nicht, Politik von selbst zu produzieren. Was es "
"produziert, ist etwas Fundamentaleres:"

#: app/templates/about.html:270
msgid "Evidence-based understanding of public opinion"
msgstr "Evidenzgestütztes Verständnis der öffentlichen Meinung"

#: app/templates/about.html:276
msgid "Clarity on where consensus exists"
msgstr "Klarheit darüber, wo Konsens besteht"

#: app/templates/about.html:282
msgid "Visibility into bridge ideas that can unite groups"
msgstr "Sichtbarkeit von Brückenideen, die Gruppen verbinden können"

#: app/templates/about.html:288
msgid "Honesty about genuine divisions that require deeper work"
msgstr "Ehrlichkeit über echte Divisionen, die tiefere Arbeit erfordern"

#: app/templates/about.html:292
msgid ""
"That insight can inform policymakers, journalists, civic organisations, and "
"anyone trying to design solutions that are both ambitious and legitimate. "
"Better policy starts with better understanding. Society Speaks focuses on "
"that first step."
msgstr ""
"Dieser Einblick kann Policymaker, Journalist*innen, Bürgerinitiativen und "
"alle informieren, die versuchen, Lösungen zu gestalten, die sowohl ehrgeizig"
" als auch legitim sind. Bessere Politik beginnt mit besserem Verständnis. "
"Society Speaks konzentriert sich auf diesen ersten Schritt."

#: app/templates/about.html:301
msgid "Built in the Open"
msgstr "Im Offenen gebaut"

#: app/templates/about.html:303
msgid ""
"Society Speaks is proudly open source. Our entire codebase is available on "
