msgid "Vote on statements"
msgstr "Stimmen Sie über Aussagen ab"

#: app/templates/index.html:105
msgid ""
"Vote Agree, Disagree, or Unsure on each statement. Add your reasoning if you"
" wish. Participation is respectful by design and anonymous if you prefer."
msgstr ""
