msgstr "Wie unterscheidet sich das von ChatGPT oder Perplexity?"

#: app/templates/briefing/landing.html:77
#: app/templates/briefing/landing.html:1279
msgid ""
"Those tools answer questions. We monitor sources and deliver briefings on a "
"schedule. You're not searching — you're being briefed on what changed since "
"yesterday."
msgstr ""
"Diese Tools beantworten Fragen. Wir überwachen Quellen und liefern Briefings"
